  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Coronavirus (COVID-19): requirements to provide public health information to passengers travelling to England
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Information that transport operators must ensure is provided to passengers and how to provide it.</p>

  </div>
</div>

